Interface RepartModule

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
RepartModuleImpl
public interface RepartModule
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Repart Module'. Rappresenta un modulo di artefatti disponibile sul repository degli artefatti.

The following features are supported:

  • Organization
  • Name
  • Version
  • Type
  • Artifacts

See Also:
GuigenPackage.getRepartModule()
